Galaxy AI is a set of features that can make Samsung Galaxy devices easier to use. These features include: 
 
Interpreter: Translates live conversations on a split-screen view so that both parties can read a text transcription. The Interpreter app can be set up by opening the Quick setting panel, selecting Interpreter, and then choosing the languages for each speaker. 
 
Android Auto: Summarizes incoming messages and suggests relevant replies and actions.

Chat Assist: A feature that can be used on Galaxy phones and tablets.
